Connecting to the regular WebTV service

When you first turn on the WebTV box it will connect to the WebTV service.

If the WebTV box has trouble connecting, check if you need to dial "9" to
get to an outside line. If you do, then you will have to use the "Basic"
phone settings to configure this feature.

Once you have connected to WebTV, you will be presented with a short
tutorial on how to use the remote control.

After the tutorial, you will be asked to sign up for the service. There are
several options, but basically you have to pay $20 per month.

Once you have gone through the sign-up process, you will arrive at the "Web
Home Page".
